articles.author: Katie Bo Lillis, Natasha Bertrand, Oren Liebermann, Haley Britzky
articles.title: Exclusive: Russia producing three times more artillery shells than US and Europe for Ukraine - CNN
articles.description: Russia appears on track to produce nearly three times more artillery munitions than the US and Europe, a key advantage ahead of what is expected to be another Russian offensive in Ukraine later this year.
